WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:02.640
June 2010.

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:06.640
I landed for the first time
in Rome, Italy.

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.696
I wasn't there to sightsee.

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:12.840
I was there to solve world hunger.

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:15.256
(Laughter)

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:16.496
That's right.

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:18.616
I was a 25-year-old PhD student

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:21.736
armed with a prototype tool
developed back at my university,

00:00:21.760 --> 00:00:24.840
and I was going to help
the World Food Programme fix hunger.

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.576
So I strode into the headquarters building

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:31.416
and my eyes scanned the row of UN flags,